## 6. STUB PATTERN for post-MVP

For every post-MVP feature that has an endpoint — the endpoint must exist but may return a stub:

```python
# routers/scheduler.py
@router.post("/admin/scheduler/run/{task_name}")
@require_role("admin")
async def manual_trigger(task_name: str):
    # TODO: post-MVP — implement APScheduler manual trigger
    return {"status": "stub", "message": f"Task {task_name} is not yet implemented"}
```

```jsx
// pages/admin/SchedulerLog.jsx
export default function SchedulerLog() {
  // TODO: post-MVP
  return <ComingSoon feature="Scheduler log" />
}
```

The `<ComingSoon>` component must exist as a reusable UI element that renders a placeholder without errors.
